relationships can be.

06:52.074 --> 06:53.674
<i>We both saw The Notebook.</i>

06:53.725 --> 06:56.343
Do you want to know how
I picture the end of my life?

06:56.395 --> 06:59.563
<i>Just like in The Notebook,
I'm sitting in a nursing home,</i>

06:59.648 --> 07:02.149
talking endlessly about
my high school sweetheart--

07:02.200 --> 07:03.567
my first love--

07:03.652 --> 07:05.703
going on and on about
every little detail,

07:05.787 --> 07:07.071
as if they matter.

07:07.155 --> 07:10.708
Only, in my version,
he's there with me,

07:10.792 --> 07:12.660
telling me to shut up
so he can finish watching

07:12.711 --> 07:15.212
