salute to J-Lo.

07:15.297 --> 07:18.082
So... we're going
to be all right?

07:18.166 --> 07:19.700
Yes, we're gonna
be all right.

07:19.751 --> 07:22.253
I told you I'm never
saying goodbye to you.

07:22.337 --> 07:25.089
We'll figure out this
whole long-distance
relationship thing.

07:25.173 --> 07:27.174
I promise.

07:27.225 --> 07:29.093
Okay.

07:31.063 --> 07:32.430
