07:32.514 --> 07:33.881
going to say goodbye
to everyone else?

07:33.932 --> 07:36.100
(school bell rings)

07:36.184 --> 07:39.553
I wanted to dedicate my
goodbye song to all of you,

07:39.604 --> 07:42.289
