thank the men in the room

07:42.357 --> 07:44.575
who have truly inspired me

07:44.660 --> 07:46.911
and never saw me for the things
that made us different.

07:46.995 --> 07:50.364
You only saw me for the ways
that we're the same.

07:50.415 --> 07:52.283
Because, in this room...

07:52.367 --> 07:55.503
it doesn't matter
if you're gay or straight...

07:55.570 --> 07:57.555
