Okay, so I called
Pace and NYADA

10:12.057 --> 10:14.592
and they sent out out
acceptance letters this week.

10:14.676 --> 10:16.477
Oh, my God,
that's so exciting.

10:16.544 --> 10:18.429
And, like,
totally terrifying.

10:18.513 --> 10:19.480
We need to make a pact.

10:19.547 --> 10:20.481
When we get our letters,

10:20.548 --> 10:21.398
we open them together,

10:21.483 --> 10:22.817
in the choir room.

10:22.884 --> 10:25.186
These letters, you know,
they're, like our future

10:25.237 --> 10:26.487
so I want to open mine

10:26.554 --> 10:28.022
with my two most
important people.

10:28.073 --> 10:29.690
Deal?
Deal.

10:29.741 --> 10:31.158
Deal.

10:31.226 --> 10:32.059
Pinkie swear?

10:32.110 --> 10:32.776
Yeah.

10:32.861 --> 10:33.727
All right.

10:35.767 --> 10:35.767
+

