10:41.698 --> 10:42.814
What is this crap?
Oh, didn't you hear?

10:42.866 --> 10:44.416
Mercedes got a
recording contract.

10:44.483 --> 10:45.701
She's moving to Hollywood
and she's going to be

10:45.785 --> 10:47.002
a superstar by Christmas,
guaranteed.

10:47.086 --> 10:48.170
MERCEDES:
He's exaggerating.

10:48.254 --> 10:49.788
You remember that video that

10:49.839 --> 10:52.090
he posted of me on YouTube,
singing "Disco Inferno"?

10:52.158 --> 10:53.125
Well, this music producer
in L.A. saw it

10:53.176 --> 10:54.326
and he wants to sign her.

10:54.377 --> 10:56.211
